 \"It comes as boxerImane Kheliffaces an international gender rowamid a frenzy of misinformation.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Italian boxer Angela Cariniabandoned the last-16 contest against her Algerian opponent after just 46 seconds, when Khelif landed the first significant punch of the fight.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9967109672608112, \"rank\": 0.0022943612612598367, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9983095150978964, \"rank\": 0.0013112956790504488, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini said she was unable to continue for fears of her safety after suffering what she described as the hardest punch of her life.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9953924979578253, \"rank\": 0.0046288293830604186, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italian's reaction led to a social media pile-on, with some accusing her opponent of being a trans woman, because she has previously failed a gender test due to a medical condition.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9967109672608112, \"rank\": 0.0022943612612598367, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc